@Comment:	Time is 18:58
@Comment:	more book reading by Chi with Sis. Mot comes in every once in a while. Chi says she wants to continue , MOT says they can take a rest afterwards. At about 39:00 when Chi sings an interesting version of It's a Small World After All then goes back to reading , with Sis's help. This goes on , with a few distractions (but without Mot). They finish the Care Bears story at 45:03 , then Chi announces I'm gonna do something else , and starts to sing America , Yankee Doodle , and other patriotic hits. The recording ends at 46:50 with those famous last words , Can we listen to it?
@End
